snippet.title: Arma 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more at http://arma2.com/
Buy now http://store.bistudio.com/arma2

We had to re-upload this video trailer due to a requirements of ESRB agency (rating descriptor added).

First ARMA 2 ingame trailer in HD, originally released in November 2008.
